Third-party code bundled in this repository:

- vendor/QL6502-src/ : MIT-licensed CPU 6502 assembler/disassembler
  by forthchina (https://github.com/forthchina/QL6502).
  See vendor/QL6502-src/ for the original sources.

External Python dependencies (installed separately, see requirements.txt) :

- py65 (Mike Naberezny) — BSD-3-Clause — https://github.com/mnaberez/py65
- typer (tiangolo)      — MIT             — https://github.com/tiangolo/typer
- cynes (Youlixx)       — MIT             — https://github.com/Youlixx/cynes
- Pillow                — HPND-style      — https://python-pillow.org/

Test fixtures :

- tests/fixtures/nestest.nes : test ROM par Kevin Horton (2004), domaine
  public — distribuée via le repository christopherpow/nes-test-roms.
